<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer14607452326807274205">Hirai Tarō (平井 太郎), better known by the pseudonym Rampo <b>Edogawa</b> (<a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/1286774._______' title=' 江戸川 乱歩' rel='nofollow noopener'> 江戸川 乱歩</a>), sometimes romanized as &quot;Ranpo Edogawa&quot;, was a Japanese author and critic who played a major role in the development of Japanese mystery fiction.</span>
  <span id="freeText14607452326807274205" style="display:none">Hirai Tarō (平井 太郎), better known by the pseudonym Rampo <b>Edogawa</b> (<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/1286774._______" title=" 江戸川 乱歩" rel="nofollow noopener"> 江戸川 乱歩</a>), sometimes romanized as "Ranpo Edogawa", was a Japanese author and critic who played a major role in the development of Japanese mystery fiction.</span>
